1
00:00:00,333 --> 00:00:02,600
today we are going to play NomiFactory

2
00:00:03,066 --> 00:00:05,100
after claiming our welcome tablet

3
00:00:05,133 --> 00:00:08,666
we quickly use its scanner app to find some diamonds

4
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,266
which we can collect with our gifted hammer

5
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:12,933
and to celebrate our wealth

6
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:15,266
we have also been given some cake

7
00:00:15,966 --> 00:00:19,500
apparently eating with dirty hands gave us hallucinations

8
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:24,300
so we started building a platform of stone to avoid falling in our dreams

9
00:00:24,533 --> 00:00:31,766
on this new foundation, we shall start laying down the first furnaces and chests to store all of the materials we just mined

10
00:00:32,366 --> 00:00:35,166
with that stuff we make our first steam machinery

11
00:00:35,166 --> 00:00:39,133
required to craft a Bricked Blast Furnace to get access to steel

12
00:00:39,766 --> 00:00:43,800
and acquiring steel means that we can now build LV machinery

13
00:00:44,266 --> 00:00:47,066
which we use to build an Electric Blast Furnace

14
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:50,900
which, as usual, we shall power with solar boilers

15
00:00:51,466 --> 00:00:54,066
and with that, we are now in the MV age

16
00:00:54,366 --> 00:00:57,333
to progress further, we will need some polyethylene

17
00:00:57,466 --> 00:01:00,900
which was also the only thing we needed to unlock AE2

18
00:01:01,333 --> 00:01:06,333
and that will be of great help inside our new clean room to craft the complex new circuits

19
00:01:06,666 --> 00:01:10,333
and the first usage for our new circuitry is a Vacuum Freezer

20
00:01:10,566 --> 00:01:12,700
which will allow us to harden titanium

21
00:01:12,766 --> 00:01:18,300
and with that we can now craft a drill capable of mining the whole height of a vein in a single click

22
00:01:18,500 --> 00:01:24,866
that way, we can easily gather the materials required to expand our solar boiler generator setup

23
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:29,000
but those Large Steam Turbines didn't last longer than their rotors

24
00:01:29,366 --> 00:01:32,266
because we already have a Large Combustion Engine

25
00:01:32,866 --> 00:01:36,866
however, we can't run it because we don't have an appropriate dynamo hatch

26
00:01:36,933 --> 00:01:39,366
and making one is a whole new rabbit hole

27
00:01:39,366 --> 00:01:44,766
which starts from making rocket fuel to send a micro miner in a pocket microverse

28
00:01:44,766 --> 00:01:48,400
however, after purifying the tungsten and mixing it with steel

29
00:01:48,666 --> 00:01:53,533
we figure out we have to upgrade our EBF to RTM coils in order to melt it

30
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:56,933
and to get those we only lack of ruthenium

31
00:01:57,100 --> 00:02:00,300
so we quickly improvise the first half of a platline

32
00:02:00,566 --> 00:02:03,400
with that we can now get the RTM coils

33
00:02:03,766 --> 00:02:08,133
thus smelt the tungsten steel for a dynamo for our combustion generator

34
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:12,966
to power it, we only use the best fuel, high octane gasoline

35
00:02:13,333 --> 00:02:16,366
and that made our old solar boiler setup obsolete

36
00:02:16,966 --> 00:02:20,166
since it's in the way, we shall do some cleanup 

37
00:02:20,466 --> 00:02:25,100
and we can use all of that space we just made for our new PBI production plant

38
00:02:25,466 --> 00:02:29,366
next we make some more multiblocks to expand our workshop

39
00:02:29,366 --> 00:02:33,966
however, it turns out that some recipes can't be done in the wild like that

40
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:37,400
so we built a proper environment around the delicate machines

41
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,933
now the issue was that the light bulbs kept popping

42
00:02:41,066 --> 00:02:44,600
to get enough material for all of those and the future upgrades

43
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:47,766
we made a huge ore processing and sorting facility

44
00:02:48,533 --> 00:02:51,633
then to keep up with the new energy consumption

45
00:02:51,633 --> 00:02:54,366
we changed the color of the Combustion Generators

46
00:02:54,666 --> 00:02:57,933
but our old cables couldn't keep up with that much power

47
00:02:58,466 --> 00:03:02,600
so we made a power substation to properly split it across all of our base

48
00:03:03,066 --> 00:03:05,533
now we have powerful machines for everything

49
00:03:05,766 --> 00:03:08,866
but those aren't better than the single block version yet

50
00:03:09,266 --> 00:03:13,400
to make them stand out, we need Parallel Control Hatches

51
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:17,066
however, crafting those will require a lot of nether stars

52
00:03:17,466 --> 00:03:19,600
and since we are playing in hard mode

53
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,566
we are locked in peaceful difficulty

54
00:03:22,066 --> 00:03:24,066
that means no wither farms

55
00:03:24,066 --> 00:03:28,400
so the best way to obtain these is to get them from another universe

56
00:03:28,933 --> 00:03:33,866
thus, we equip our tier 4 Microverse Mining Drone with some swords to do the task

57
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:36,433
making it tier four and a half

58
00:03:36,433 --> 00:03:40,233
once built, we send it in our slightly bigger version of microverse

59
00:03:40,233 --> 00:03:42,366
and we wait for the loot to come back

60
00:03:42,933 --> 00:03:46,500
finally, we use all of those rods to craft a nether star

61
00:03:46,966 --> 00:03:50,400
moving on, the next full tier rocket is the tier 5

62
00:03:50,566 --> 00:03:52,566
but this one will need better fuel

63
00:03:52,733 --> 00:03:54,133
such as plutonium

64
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:57,100
after quickly diving deep into nuclear craft

65
00:03:57,133 --> 00:03:58,766
we managed to salvage some

66
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:00,966
which we use to power our new rocket

67
00:04:00,966 --> 00:04:04,866
and get some minerals from which we can extract naquadah

68
00:04:04,866 --> 00:04:08,466
with that, we can make coils capable of melting trinium

69
00:04:08,666 --> 00:04:10,533
which makes even better coils

70
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,500
and it doesn't stop there

71
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:16,166
with trinium we can also make superconducting coils

72
00:04:16,733 --> 00:04:18,566
those aren't for a blast furnace

73
00:04:18,566 --> 00:04:21,933
but for something that will be built by our new Assembly Line

74
00:04:21,933 --> 00:04:23,466
a Fusion Reactor

75
00:04:24,066 --> 00:04:26,733
this is a huge toroidal structure that

76
00:04:26,733 --> 00:04:28,966
after charging up with a lot of energy

77
00:04:28,966 --> 00:04:34,033
will start fusing light elements to create new ones that can't be found in nature

78
00:04:34,033 --> 00:04:35,066
such as europium

79
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:39,000
and with that new material we can start crystallizing some chips

80
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:42,466
that can be used to go beyond the limitations of silicon

81
00:04:42,566 --> 00:04:45,500
making a new series of more advanced processors

82
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:53,766
however, single steps of those circuits and their components are starting to take way more energy than our combustion generator could produce

83
00:04:54,266 --> 00:04:55,366
to fix that issue

84
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,766
we added some powerful solar panels

85
00:04:57,900 --> 00:04:59,900
but those didn't keep up for long

86
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:03,166
one of the main issues is that they don't always work

87
00:05:03,566 --> 00:05:05,466
and as the sun sets

88
00:05:05,566 --> 00:05:06,900
we take a deep breath

89
00:05:07,566 --> 00:05:14,500
then we exhale our blazing pyrotheum and high octane gasoline dragon breath on some metal dust to make it draconic

90
00:05:14,933 --> 00:05:19,500
we give that dust a quick heating in our blast furnace with the addition of some gasoline

91
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:21,900
and cool it down into an ingot

92
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:27,100
we make this material pass multiple times inside our new Fusion Crafter

93
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:30,666
until we manage to craft a new tier of rocket out of it

94
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:34,366
and this one requires a new tier of Microverse Projector

95
00:05:34,766 --> 00:05:37,500
this time we will be scouting for dragon hearts

96
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:42,200
which we shall use to make a Celestial Manipulator to make the nights fly away

97
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:44,800
and the way this machine actually works

98
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:49,400
is by distracting us with cool animations for long enough for the sun to rise naturally

99
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:51,766
anyways, after all of that

100
00:05:51,766 --> 00:05:54,700
we can go back to our research for new materials

101
00:05:54,933 --> 00:05:56,666
and what we found out is that

102
00:05:56,666 --> 00:05:58,800
with a new tier of Fusion Reactor

103
00:05:58,933 --> 00:06:00,400
we can get tritanium

104
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:05,766
and the first thing we can do with it is to upgrade our Clean Room into a Sterile Room

105
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:08,900
however, since that upgrade was expensive

106
00:06:09,066 --> 00:06:11,000
we made a smaller one on the side

107
00:06:11,366 --> 00:06:15,133
and we made sure to optimize the space we have inside it

108
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,666
with this new sterile environment

109
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,866
we can now make stem cells

110
00:06:19,866 --> 00:06:23,133
as usual, making progress will make the sheep poor

111
00:06:23,666 --> 00:06:25,333
sorry, fat cows medditors

112
00:06:25,466 --> 00:06:26,666
but we shall ignore it

113
00:06:26,666 --> 00:06:28,733
and move on to our old clean room

114
00:06:28,933 --> 00:06:31,800
where we can make the best circuit boards available

115
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:37,266
then we build some neuroprocessing boards on those for our new wetware circuits

116
00:06:37,266 --> 00:06:41,300
however, we are not yet capable of clustering those into a mainframe

117
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:45,466
that is because we do not have enough computation power for that research

118
00:06:45,666 --> 00:06:47,600
so we upgrade our computer

119
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,533
but that was still not enough

120
00:06:49,766 --> 00:06:53,466
so we built a Network Switch to chain even more computers together

121
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:56,933
thus reaching the needed computation for our new circuit

122
00:06:57,266 --> 00:06:59,866
this data orb is bigger than the previous ones

123
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:03,000
so it has to be read by a data bank to be used

124
00:07:03,466 --> 00:07:08,200
and with that, we now have unlocked the highest tier of circuit in the game

125
00:07:08,533 --> 00:07:12,200
which we shall use to make the highest tier of Fusion Reactor

126
00:07:12,333 --> 00:07:18,100
which will allow us to produce the material required for the highest tier of Micro Universe Harvester

127
00:07:18,333 --> 00:07:20,133
but it's not enough on its own

128
00:07:20,533 --> 00:07:22,966
and of all of the materials required

129
00:07:23,266 --> 00:07:24,966
the one we miss is omnium

130
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:28,366
which is an amalgamate of every early game material

131
00:07:28,666 --> 00:07:32,166
so, after collecting a stack of each one of those materials

132
00:07:32,366 --> 00:07:35,400
we managed to finally build the highest tier of rocket

133
00:07:35,533 --> 00:07:37,766
which produced the half of an universe

134
00:07:37,966 --> 00:07:41,533
the first use we have for those is Stabilizing Micro Miners

135
00:07:42,066 --> 00:07:45,533
this will make them strong enough to come back from their missions

136
00:07:45,533 --> 00:07:48,000
thus giving us virtually infinite goodies

137
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:53,366
all at the cost of building one extra multiblock with the cost of about half a Fusion Reactor

138
00:07:53,366 --> 00:07:57,000
and with that, we can go back on our road to the infinity ingot

139
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,866
and you might notice there is no infinite tank here

140
00:08:00,866 --> 00:08:04,300
so instead of the iconic fluid solidifier spam

141
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:06,133
we shall have extractor spam

142
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,966
but we are also going to need more air collectors

143
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,700
so we get a PA

144
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:13,200
then we upgrade and even cluster it

145
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:16,233
and all of this air must be cooled with our new chiller

146
00:08:16,233 --> 00:08:18,733
and distilled with a bigger Fractionating Tower

147
00:08:19,066 --> 00:08:22,266
next we shall also build a couple more fusion reactors

148
00:08:22,533 --> 00:08:24,533
but fluids are not the only issue

149
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:27,200
we shall also have a bigger blast furnace

150
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:30,266
which we can build with the help of the new app of our tablet

151
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:34,866
this rotary half furnace is going to melt 4 stacks of items at once

152
00:08:35,066 --> 00:08:36,566
using UIV power

153
00:08:36,933 --> 00:08:41,400
and all of those items are then processed in our new Assembly Line cluster

154
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,666
to power all of those new machines

155
00:08:43,966 --> 00:08:45,466
we needed something special

156
00:08:46,066 --> 00:08:47,733
we tried various methods

157
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:50,600
but the best solution was the most simple one

158
00:08:50,766 --> 00:08:54,133
using a tick accelerator on Neutronium Solar Panels

159
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:56,733
the bottleneck is the energy converters

160
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,933
and we are already using the best kind

161
00:09:00,333 --> 00:09:05,333
also, this setup makes way more energy than our decorative disco balls combined

162
00:09:06,366 --> 00:09:09,500
and now that we fixed about all of the main issues

163
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:12,066
we can start working on the Creative Chest

164
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:15,000
to get one we will need a lot of materials

165
00:09:15,333 --> 00:09:17,200
most of them are passively produced

166
00:09:17,533 --> 00:09:19,500
so we can just wait a little bit

167
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:24,066
there are also some items for which we haven't prepared a recipe yet

168
00:09:24,266 --> 00:09:26,933
but one thing caught our attention, apples

169
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:31,800
we can get those either by opening loot boxes or with social engineering

170
00:09:32,166 --> 00:09:34,333
but rather than doing those two things

171
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:36,500
I'd say we can touch some grass

172
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:38,500
and collect apples like Newton did

173
00:09:38,533 --> 00:09:40,300
by letting them hit us on our head

174
00:09:40,466 --> 00:09:45,300
thus gaining the insight and inspiration to build a machine that does this task for us

175
00:09:45,733 --> 00:09:47,000
with that out of the way

176
00:09:47,133 --> 00:09:50,600
we can start crafting the parts of our objective one at a time

177
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,600
while trying to fix the bottlenecks

178
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:55,400
so we build more fusion reactors

179
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,366
faster solidifiers

180
00:09:57,866 --> 00:09:59,866
accelerated ultimate crafting

181
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:02,133
a second Draconic Crafter

182
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:04,400
more Microverse Projectors

183
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:06,400
more actuators

184
00:10:07,066 --> 00:10:08,933
more Alloy Blast Smelters

185
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:11,066
more Fusion Reactors

186
00:10:11,533 --> 00:10:13,600
a bigger Royal Distillery Plant

187
00:10:13,866 --> 00:10:15,500
a bigger Breeder Reactor

188
00:10:15,733 --> 00:10:18,700
a thing that simplifies annoying craftings

189
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:21,133
however, to power all of those machines

190
00:10:21,133 --> 00:10:23,733
we needed a more versatile energy source

191
00:10:24,300 --> 00:10:27,200
so we quickly craft an Infinite GT EU Emitter

192
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,400
which we set to really high settings

193
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,366
and then attach a peer to peer to

194
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:36,166
now we can start throwing 16 amps UHV energy hatches everywhere

195
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,566
or at least wherever we can

196
00:10:38,566 --> 00:10:41,266
otherwise, like with fusion reactors

197
00:10:41,533 --> 00:10:43,733
we will simply be building more of it

198
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:46,533
and now we go back to fixing bottlenecks

199
00:10:46,733 --> 00:10:48,300
such as our soul binder

200
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,566
we make more subnetted mixers

201
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,066
add some more LCR clusters

202
00:10:53,533 --> 00:10:56,333
increase our cobblestone production and storage capacity

203
00:10:56,866 --> 00:10:58,566
stare at our cobblestone stocks

204
00:10:58,766 --> 00:11:00,800
we add a bunch more crafting units

205
00:11:01,133 --> 00:11:02,800
increase our Mega Blast Furnace count

206
00:11:02,933 --> 00:11:04,400
we overclock our Nuclear Reactor

207
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,866
we increase our packaging capacity

208
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:06,966
we build more electrolyzers

209
00:11:06,966 --> 00:11:08,133
we add more Fusion Reactors

210
00:11:08,133 --> 00:11:09,266
we overhaul the plastic production

211
00:11:09,266 --> 00:11:10,100
we increase our air collection

212
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:10,633
we have many more packages

213
00:11:10,633 --> 00:11:12,000
and build more and more overclock package crafters

214
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:12,900
we build more Fusion Reactors

215
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:14,133
we increase our sugarcane farming capability

216
00:11:22,066 --> 00:11:23,933
we accelerated a full scale nuke craft reactor

217
00:11:23,933 --> 00:11:25,866
and after completing the third Fusion Tower

218
00:11:25,866 --> 00:11:28,333
we can start assembling the most expensive item of the pack

219
00:11:28,333 --> 00:11:29,600
the Creative Chest

220
00:11:30,133 --> 00:11:31,533
and since we have no time

221
00:11:31,533 --> 00:11:33,133
to waste to craft it quicker

222
00:11:33,166 --> 00:11:35,600
we are going to use the power sources of our base

223
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:38,500
and now that we put together all the pieces

224
00:11:39,066 --> 00:11:41,533
the Creative Chest is finally ours

225
00:11:42,066 --> 00:11:43,933
and with it in our hands

226
00:11:44,266 --> 00:11:47,700
we can finally say that we completed this modpack

227
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:49,800
and we can move on to the next one

228
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,266
bye bye

229
00:00:00,333 --> 00:00:02,600
今天我们要玩 NomiFactory

230
00:00:03,066 --> 00:00:05,100
在领取新手平板礼包之后

231
00:00:05,133 --> 00:00:08,666
我们很快用它的扫描功能找到了几颗钻石

232
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,266
可以用赠送的锤子收集它们

233
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:12,933
为了庆祝这泼天富贵

234
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:15,266
我们得到了些蛋糕

235
00:00:15,966 --> 00:00:19,500
显然，用脏手吃东西会让人产生幻觉

236
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:24,300
所以我们搭了块石头平台，免得在梦里跌落

237
00:00:24,533 --> 00:00:31,766
在这个新平台上，我们放下熔炉和存放刚开采的材料的箱子

238
00:00:32,366 --> 00:00:35,166
用这些材料我们造出了第一批蒸汽机械

239
00:00:35,166 --> 00:00:39,133
来造出砖高炉，用来炼钢

240
00:00:39,766 --> 00:00:43,800
有了钢，我们现在可以制造 LV 的机器了

241
00:00:44,266 --> 00:00:47,066
用来造电高炉

242
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:50,900
一如既往，我们用太阳能锅炉给它供能

243
00:00:51,466 --> 00:00:54,066
就这样，我们进入了 MV 时代

244
00:00:54,366 --> 00:00:57,333
要继续发展，我们需要一些聚乙烯

245
00:00:57,466 --> 00:01:00,900
这也是解锁 AE2 的唯一前置条件

246
00:01:01,333 --> 00:01:06,333
这对我们在新洁净间里制作复杂电路帮助很大

247
00:01:06,666 --> 00:01:10,333
新电路的第一个用途是制造真空冷冻机

248
00:01:10,566 --> 00:01:12,700
它能让我们硬化钛

249
00:01:12,766 --> 00:01:18,300
有了它，我们能做出一次点击就能挖完整条矿脉的电钻

250
00:01:18,500 --> 00:01:24,866
这样我们就能轻松收集扩建太阳能锅炉所需的材料

251
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:29,000
但那些大型蒸汽涡轮的寿命甚至不如转子

252
00:01:29,366 --> 00:01:32,266
因为我们有了一台大型内燃机

253
00:01:32,866 --> 00:01:36,866
不过我们无法运行它——我们缺少合适的动力仓

254
00:01:36,933 --> 00:01:39,366
制作它又是另一个大坑

255
00:01:39,366 --> 00:01:44,766
从制造火箭燃料、把微型矿机送入袖珍微宇宙开始

256
00:01:44,766 --> 00:01:48,400
但在提纯钨并与钢混合后

257
00:01:48,666 --> 00:01:53,533
我们发现必须把 EBF 升级为 RTM 线圈才能熔化它

258
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:56,933
而要获得这些线圈，我们只差钌

259
00:01:57,100 --> 00:02:00,300
于是我们快速做了铂处理的前半段

260
00:02:00,566 --> 00:02:03,400
有了它我们就能拿到 RTM 线圈

261
00:02:03,766 --> 00:02:08,133
从而熔炼出用于内燃发电机的动力仓的钨钢

262
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:12,966
我们只打算用最好的燃料“高辛烷值汽油”给它供能

263
00:02:13,333 --> 00:02:16,366
这让旧的太阳能锅炉装置变得多余

264
00:02:16,966 --> 00:02:20,166
既然碍事，我们就清理掉它

265
00:02:20,466 --> 00:02:25,100
把腾出的空间用来建新的 PBI 工厂

266
00:02:25,466 --> 00:02:29,366
接着我们做更多多方块机器来扩展车间

267
00:02:29,366 --> 00:02:33,966
不过有些配方不能露天完成

268
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:37,400
因此我们为精密机器搭建了合适的环境

269
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,933
当时的问题是灯泡老是爆

270
00:02:41,066 --> 00:02:44,600
为了给这些灯泡和未来的升级获取足够的材料

271
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:47,766
我们建了个大型矿石加工与分拣设施

272
00:02:48,533 --> 00:02:51,633
接着，为应对新增的电力需求

273
00:02:51,633 --> 00:02:54,366
我们更换了内燃发电机的颜色

274
00:02:54,666 --> 00:02:57,933
但旧电缆承载不了那么多电力

275
00:02:58,466 --> 00:03:02,600
所以我们建了个变电站，把电力合理分配到基地各处

276
00:03:03,066 --> 00:03:05,533
现在我们有了各种强力机器

277
00:03:05,766 --> 00:03:08,866
但它们还未必比单方块版本更强

278
00:03:09,266 --> 00:03:13,400
要让它们变强，我们需要并行控制仓

279
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:17,066
然而制作这些需要大量下界之星

280
00:03:17,466 --> 00:03:19,600
而我们是在硬核模式下游玩

281
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,566
被锁在和平难度里

282
00:03:22,066 --> 00:03:24,066
这意味着不能建凋灵农场

283
00:03:24,066 --> 00:03:28,400
所以最好的办法就是从另一个宇宙取得它们

284
00:03:28,933 --> 00:03:33,866
于是我们给四阶微宇宙采矿无人机配了把剑去完成任务

285
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:36,433
把它变成了四阶半

286
00:03:36,433 --> 00:03:40,233
做好后把它送进稍大一点的微宇宙

287
00:03:40,233 --> 00:03:42,366
然后等着战利品回来

288
00:03:42,933 --> 00:03:46,500
最后我们用那些棒子合成了一颗下界之星

289
00:03:46,966 --> 00:03:50,400
接下来的完整阶火箭是 5 阶

290
00:03:50,566 --> 00:03:52,566
但那需要更好的燃料

291
00:03:52,733 --> 00:03:54,133
比如钚

292
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:57,100
在快速深入核制造之后

293
00:03:57,133 --> 00:03:58,766
我们设法回收到一些材料

294
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:00,966
用来为新火箭供能

295
00:04:00,966 --> 00:04:04,866
并获取了可以提取出硅岩的矿物

296
00:04:04,866 --> 00:04:08,466
有了它我们能制造出能熔化三元金属的线圈

297
00:04:08,666 --> 00:04:10,533
从而做出更高阶的线圈

298
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,500
而且这还没完

299
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:16,166
我们还能用三元金属制造超导线圈

300
00:04:16,733 --> 00:04:18,566
这些不是给高炉用的

301
00:04:18,566 --> 00:04:21,933
而是给我们新装配线将要做的东西准备的

302
00:04:21,933 --> 00:04:23,466
也就是聚变堆

303
00:04:24,066 --> 00:04:26,733
它是一个巨大的环形结构

304
00:04:26,733 --> 00:04:28,966
在注入大量能量后

305
00:04:28,966 --> 00:04:34,033
会开始将轻元素聚变成自然界中不存在的新元素

306
00:04:34,033 --> 00:04:35,066
比如铕

307
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:39,000
凭借这种新材料我们可以开始制作晶体芯片

308
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:42,466
用于突破硅基的限制

309
00:04:42,566 --> 00:04:45,500
打造一系列更先进的处理器

310
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:53,766
但那类电路及其组件的单步能耗已经远超我们的内燃发电机

311
00:04:54,266 --> 00:04:55,366
为了解决这个问题

312
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,766
我们增加了一些高功率太阳能板

313
00:04:57,900 --> 00:04:59,900
但它们很快就跟不上了

314
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:03,166
主要问题之一是它们并不总是可用

315
00:05:03,566 --> 00:05:05,466
当太阳落下时

316
00:05:05,566 --> 00:05:06,900
我们深吸一口气

317
00:05:07,566 --> 00:05:14,500
然后对一些金属粉呼出烈焰之炽焱与高辛烷值汽油的“龙息”，让它变成龙级材料

318
00:05:14,933 --> 00:05:19,500
在高炉里快速加热该粉末并加入少量汽油

319
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:21,900
再冷却成锭

320
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:27,100
我们让这种材料在新的龙研聚合装置中多次加工

321
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:30,666
直到用它制造出五阶的火箭

322
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:34,366
这次需要更高阶的微宇宙投影仪

323
00:05:34,766 --> 00:05:37,500
这次我们要去搜寻龙心

324
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:42,200
用它做天体操纵器，把夜晚赶走

325
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:44,800
这台机器的实际做法是

326
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:49,400
用炫酷的动画把我们一直吸引住，等太阳自然升起

327
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:51,766
不管怎样，完成这些之后

328
00:05:51,766 --> 00:05:54,700
我们可以回去继续研究新材料

329
00:05:54,933 --> 00:05:56,666
我们发现

330
00:05:56,666 --> 00:05:58,800
有了新一阶的聚变堆

331
00:05:58,933 --> 00:06:00,400
我们可以获得三钛

332
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:05,766
我们用它做的第一件事是把洁净间升级为无菌室

333
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:08,900
然而，由于那项升级成本很高

334
00:06:09,066 --> 00:06:11,000
我们在旁边建了一个小一点的版本

335
00:06:11,366 --> 00:06:15,133
并对内部空间进行了优化

336
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,666
有了这个新的无菌环境

337
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,866
我们现在可以制造干细胞了

338
00:06:19,866 --> 00:06:23,133
像往常一样，进步会让羊变穷

339
00:06:23,666 --> 00:06:25,333
抱歉，是肥牛调解员

340
00:06:25,466 --> 00:06:26,666
但我们会忽略它

341
00:06:26,666 --> 00:06:28,733
接着回到我们原来的洁净间

342
00:06:28,933 --> 00:06:31,800
在那里我们可以制造出最好的电路板

343
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:37,266
然后我们在其上制作神经元处理器基板，用于新的湿件电路

344
00:06:37,266 --> 00:06:41,300
然而，我们还不能将它们集成成主机

345
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:45,466
那是因为我们的研究算力还不够

346
00:06:45,666 --> 00:06:47,600
所以我们升级了计算机

347
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,533
但这仍然不够

348
00:06:49,766 --> 00:06:53,466
于是我们搭建了一个网络交换机，将更多计算机串联起来

349
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:56,933
从而为我们的新电路板提供所需的算力

350
00:06:57,266 --> 00:06:59,866
这个数据球比之前的大得多

351
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:03,000
因此必须由数据库来读取才能使用

352
00:07:03,466 --> 00:07:08,200
有了它我们就解锁了游戏中最高阶的电路板

353
00:07:08,533 --> 00:07:12,200
我们将用它来制造最高阶的聚变堆

354
00:07:12,333 --> 00:07:18,100
这将使我们能够生产最高阶微宇宙采矿机所需的材料

355
00:07:18,333 --> 00:07:20,133
但单靠它还不够

356
00:07:20,533 --> 00:07:22,966
在所有所需材料中

357
00:07:23,266 --> 00:07:24,966
我们缺少的就是 Omnium

358
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:28,366
它是所有早期游戏材料的混合物

359
00:07:28,666 --> 00:07:32,166
因此，在收集了每种材料的一整堆之后

360
00:07:32,366 --> 00:07:35,400
我们终于成功建造了最高阶的火箭

361
00:07:35,533 --> 00:07:37,766
它产出了一半的宇宙

362
00:07:37,966 --> 00:07:41,533
我们最先用它来稳定微型矿机

363
00:07:42,066 --> 00:07:45,533
这能让它们强到能从任务中带着战利品回来

364
00:07:45,533 --> 00:07:48,000
从而给我们几乎无限的资源

365
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:53,366
所有这些以建设一个额外多方块为代价，成本大约相当于半座聚变堆

366
00:07:53,366 --> 00:07:57,000
有了这些，我们就能回到通往无限锭的道路上

367
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,866
你可能会注意到这里没有无限水槽

368
00:08:00,866 --> 00:08:04,300
因此我们不会用标志性的流体固化器去刷屏

369
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:06,133
而是采用提取器刷屏

370
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,966
但我们还需要更多的空气收集器

371
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,700
所以我们弄了一个 PA

372
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:13,200
然后对它进行升级，甚至集群化

373
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:16,233
所有这些空气都要通过我们的新冷却器冷却

374
00:08:16,233 --> 00:08:18,733
并用更大的分馏塔进行蒸馏

375
00:08:19,066 --> 00:08:22,266
接下来我们还会建造几座聚变堆

376
00:08:22,533 --> 00:08:24,533
但液体并不是唯一的问题

377
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:27,200
我们还要一座更大的高炉

378
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:30,266
我们可以借助平板电脑的新应用来建造它

379
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:34,866
这个旋转半炉一次会熔化整整四堆物品

380
00:08:35,066 --> 00:08:36,566
使用 UIV 电力

381
00:08:36,933 --> 00:08:41,400
然后这些物品会在我们的新装配线集群中被加工处理

382
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,666
为所有这些新机器提供动力

383
00:08:43,966 --> 00:08:45,466
为此我们需要一些特殊手段

384
00:08:46,066 --> 00:08:47,733
我们尝试了各种方法

385
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:50,600
但最好的解决办法往往是最简单的

386
00:08:50,766 --> 00:08:54,133
在中子太阳能电池板上使用滴答加速器

387
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:56,733
真正的瓶颈是能量转换器

388
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,933
而我们已经在使用最好的那种了

389
00:09:00,333 --> 00:09:05,333
而且，这套系统产生的能量远超过我们那些装饰性迪斯科球的总和

390
00:09:06,366 --> 00:09:09,500
现在我们已经解决了大部分主要问题

391
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:12,066
可以开始着手制作创意箱了

392
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:15,000
要做出一个创意箱，我们需要大量材料

393
00:09:15,333 --> 00:09:17,200
而其中大多数是被动产出的

394
00:09:17,533 --> 00:09:19,500
所以我们可以稍微等一段时间

395
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:24,066
还有一些物品的配方我们尚未准备好

396
00:09:24,266 --> 00:09:26,933
但有一件事引起了我们的注意：苹果

397
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:31,800
我们可以通过开战利品箱或进行社交工程来获取它们

398
00:09:32,166 --> 00:09:34,333
但我们并不打算采用这两种方法

399
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:36,500
我想我们可以去“碰点草”（touch some grass）

400
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:38,500
像牛顿那样收集苹果

401
00:09:38,533 --> 00:09:40,300
让它们砸到我们的头上

402
00:09:40,466 --> 00:09:45,300
从而获得灵感，去造一台替我们完成这项任务的机器

403
00:09:45,733 --> 00:09:47,000
有了它之后

404
00:09:47,133 --> 00:09:50,600
我们就可以开始逐一制作目标所需的部件

405
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,600
同时修复那些瓶颈

406
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:55,400
所以我们建造了更多聚变堆

407
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,366
更快的固化器

408
00:09:57,866 --> 00:09:59,866
加速终极合成

409
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:02,133
第二台龙级制造器

410
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:04,400
更多微宇宙投影仪

411
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:06,400
更多执行器

412
00:10:07,066 --> 00:10:08,933
更多合金高炉

413
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:11,066
更多聚变堆

414
00:10:11,533 --> 00:10:13,600
更大的皇家酿酒厂

415
00:10:13,866 --> 00:10:15,500
更大的增殖反应堆

416
00:10:15,733 --> 00:10:18,700
一个用来简化繁琐合成的装置

417
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:21,133
然而，为了驱动所有这些机器

418
00:10:21,133 --> 00:10:23,733
我们需要更通用的能源来源

419
00:10:24,300 --> 00:10:27,200
于是我们快速制作了一个无限 GT EU 发射器

420
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,400
并把它调到非常高的设置

421
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,366
然后接上点对点（peer-to-peer）连接

422
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:36,166
现在我们可以到处放置 16 安培的 UHV 能量舱口

423
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,566
至少把它们放到可用位置

424
00:10:38,566 --> 00:10:41,266
否则，就像对待聚变堆那样

425
00:10:41,533 --> 00:10:43,733
我们就干脆再建更多

426
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:46,533
现在我们又回去修复瓶颈了

427
00:10:46,733 --> 00:10:48,300
比如我们的灵魂绑定器

428
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,566
我们制造了更多子网混合器

429
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,066
并新增了更多 LCR 集群

430
00:10:53,533 --> 00:10:56,333
扩展鹅卵石的生产与存储能力

431
00:10:56,866 --> 00:10:58,566
监控我们的鹅卵石库存

432
00:10:58,766 --> 00:11:00,800
我们增加了更多工艺单元

433
00:11:01,133 --> 00:11:02,800
增加巨型高炉数量

434
00:11:02,933 --> 00:11:04,400
我们对核反应堆进行了超频

435
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,866
我们提高了打包产能

436
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:06,966
我们制造了更多电解槽

437
00:11:06,966 --> 00:11:08,133
我们建造了更多聚变堆

438
00:11:08,133 --> 00:11:09,266
我们大幅改造了塑料生产线

439
00:11:09,266 --> 00:11:10,100
我们提高了空气收集量

440
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:10,633
我们还有很多物资包要处理。

441
00:11:10,633 --> 00:11:12,000
并建立了越来越多的超频包装设施

442
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:12,900
我们又建造了更多聚变堆

443
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:14,133
我们提高了甘蔗种植产能

444
00:11:14,133 --> 00:11:22,066
（燃尽了）

445
00:11:22,066 --> 00:11:23,933
我们对一座全尺寸核反应堆进行了超频

446
00:11:23,933 --> 00:11:25,866
在完成第三座聚变塔之后

447
00:11:25,866 --> 00:11:28,333
我们就能开始组装包里最昂贵的物品了

448
00:11:28,333 --> 00:11:29,600
创意箱

449
00:11:30,133 --> 00:11:31,533
由于时间有限

450
00:11:31,533 --> 00:11:33,133
我们要迅速完成它

451
00:11:33,166 --> 00:11:35,600
我们要利用基地的能量资源

452
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:38,500
现在我们把所有部件拼装在一起

453
00:11:39,066 --> 00:11:41,533
创意箱终于属于我们了

454
00:11:42,066 --> 00:11:43,933
它已经到我们手中

455
00:11:44,266 --> 00:11:47,700
我们终于可以说，我们完成了这个模组包

